1
00:00:00,708 --> 00:00:03,946
<i>♫ The dusk awakens ♫</i>

2
00:00:04,842 --> 00:00:08,426
<i>♫ The slumber of the whales ♫</i>

3
00:00:11,946 --> 00:00:15,274
<i>♫ Swimming towards the galaxy ♫</i>

4
00:00:16,202 --> 00:00:21,066
<i>♫ It docks at the blue shore of my heart ♫</i>

5
00:00:21,066 --> 00:00:26,058
<i>♫ I hear the poems coming from afar ♫</i>

6
00:00:26,698 --> 00:00:32,298
<i>♫ Happiness and sorrow come and go ♫</i>

7
00:00:32,298 --> 00:00:37,866
<i>♫ As my memories dance along the clouds ♫</i>

8
00:00:37,866 --> 00:00:41,674
<i>♫ I still remember ♫</i>

9
00:00:43,498 --> 00:00:49,290
<i>♫ Please wait for me at the horizon ♫</i>

10
00:00:49,290 --> 00:00:52,554
<i>♫ We'll watch the sunset together ♫</i>

11
00:00:54,794 --> 00:01:00,426
<i>♫ Whose dream hasn't been beautiful ♫</i>

12
00:01:00,426 --> 00:01:04,586
<i>♫ When have I ever been myself ♫</i>

13
00:01:06,154 --> 00:01:11,914
<i>♫ Wait for me at the end of the daydream ♫</i>

14
00:01:11,914 --> 00:01:15,338
<i>♫ Who has wandered within it ♫</i>

15
00:01:17,418 --> 00:01:22,378
<i>♫ Life is nothing more than fantasy ♫</i>

16
00:01:23,242 --> 00:01:25,572
<i>♫ I am still me ♫</i>

17
00:01:25,572 --> 00:01:29,764
<i>[You Are Desire]</i>

18
00:01:29,764 --> 00:01:33,664
<i>[Episode 12 We're Never Apart]</i>

19
00:01:44,868 --> 00:01:47,068
You don't look well.

20
00:01:48,669 --> 00:01:51,709
Your uncle told me you--

21
00:01:51,709 --> 00:01:52,800
I'm fine.

22
00:01:55,628 --> 00:01:57,029
I've read

23
00:01:57,029 --> 00:01:58,148
Qinghe's medical report.

24
00:01:59,348 --> 00:02:01,769
Actually, the doctors have tried

25
00:02:01,769 --> 00:02:03,109
whatever they could do.

26
00:02:04,068 --> 00:02:05,449
It's a miracle

27
00:02:05,449 --> 00:02:07,208
that he has made it this far.

28
00:02:07,208 --> 00:02:08,508
So?

29
00:02:09,469 --> 00:02:11,068
You will sign the consent form
to stop his treatment?

30
00:02:13,869 --> 00:02:15,249
I do hope

31
00:02:15,249 --> 00:02:17,228
Qinghe can leave with dignity.

32
00:02:17,788 --> 00:02:19,029
I lean towards conservative treatment.

33
00:02:20,149 --> 00:02:21,169
I think

34
00:02:21,169 --> 00:02:22,348
that's what Qinghe wants.

35
00:02:25,029 --> 00:02:28,749
You've spent the most time with him.

36
00:02:29,948 --> 00:02:33,309
I know you two are very close.

37
00:02:33,828 --> 00:02:35,108
No one can replace him.

38
00:02:36,269 --> 00:02:38,189
I know how you feel.

39
00:02:38,189 --> 00:02:39,269
Shen Juan,

40
00:02:41,228 --> 00:02:42,788
you're an adult now.

41
00:02:44,508 --> 00:02:46,148
You have the right to make your own decisions.

42
00:02:46,148 --> 00:02:49,388
I let you make the final decision.

43
00:02:49,388 --> 00:02:51,828
This is probably what Qinghe would want.

44
00:03:00,967 --> 00:03:04,384
<i>[Consent Form for Discontinuing Treatment]</i>

45
00:03:44,068 --> 00:03:45,269
<i>I'm sorry, uncle.</i>

46
00:03:47,589 --> 00:03:49,989
<i>Juan, no need to glue it back.</i>

47
00:03:50,989 --> 00:03:53,569
<i>But this is your favorite cup.</i>

48
00:03:53,569 --> 00:03:54,749
<i>You need to know</i>

49
00:03:55,508 --> 00:03:58,828
<i>everything in this world
has to experience life and death.</i>

50
00:03:59,749 --> 00:04:01,228
<i>I believe this cup</i>

51
00:04:01,788 --> 00:04:04,429
<i>has received your apology
and known your sadness.</i>

52
00:04:06,429 --> 00:04:07,948
<i>Just let it go.</i>

53
00:04:35,829 --> 00:04:36,992
Uncle.

54
00:04:41,308 --> 00:04:43,149
Do you think I should give up on you?

55
00:05:29,188 --> 00:05:31,768
Mom, I left something in Pucheng.

56
00:05:31,768 --> 00:05:33,549
Can you contact my dad

57
00:05:33,549 --> 00:05:34,669
and ask him to mail it to me?

58
00:05:34,669 --> 00:05:37,228
What is it? I'll buy you a new one.

59
00:05:38,949 --> 00:05:41,209
Class notes. I've taken a lot.

60
00:05:41,209 --> 00:05:42,589
They are useful.

61
00:05:42,589 --> 00:05:44,268
Huaicheng High School

62
00:05:44,268 --> 00:05:45,868
is nationally famous.

63
00:05:46,949 --> 00:05:48,049
The teaching here is better

64
00:05:48,049 --> 00:05:49,748
than that of your previous high school.

65
00:05:50,548 --> 00:05:52,469
Instead of thinking about your old notes,

66
00:05:52,469 --> 00:05:54,788
you should focus on your current study.

67
00:05:56,069 --> 00:05:57,828
But I think the old ones are useful.

68
00:05:57,828 --> 00:05:59,689
Can the old and the new be compared?

69
00:05:59,689 --> 00:06:02,188
The teaching and faculty here are the best.

70
00:06:03,348 --> 00:06:06,069
The rate of students going
to top universities is the highest.

71
00:06:07,469 --> 00:06:08,889
You've been back for so long.

72
00:06:08,889 --> 00:06:10,868
Why are you still thinking about Pucheng?

73
00:06:11,589 --> 00:06:14,169
Compare your old grades with new ones,

74
00:06:14,169 --> 00:06:15,509
and you'll know the gap.

75
00:06:19,308 --> 00:06:21,669
Yu, I know you're not convinced.

76
00:06:21,669 --> 00:06:23,269
And you even blame me for this.

77
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,089
But I am telling you.

78
00:06:25,089 --> 00:06:27,269
This is the most important juncture
in your life.

79
00:06:27,788 --> 00:06:28,808
As your mother,

80
00:06:28,808 --> 00:06:30,388
I have the responsibility to keep you

81
00:06:30,388 --> 00:06:32,188
on the right path in life.

82
00:06:33,668 --> 00:06:35,489
How do you know what you do is right?

83
00:06:35,489 --> 00:06:36,689
How could I not know?

84
00:06:36,689 --> 00:06:38,629
I've been through all this.

85
00:06:40,029 --> 00:06:41,708
If you're really responsible for yourself,

86
00:06:41,708 --> 00:06:43,229
you should study hard.

87
00:06:43,229 --> 00:06:44,868
Don't think about useless stuff.

88
00:07:08,389 --> 00:07:12,129
<i>[Go for it, Juan]
It's time to move on, Juan.</i>

89
00:07:12,129 --> 00:07:15,308
<i>This is what Qinghe and your mother hope for.</i>

90
00:07:46,108 --> 00:07:49,308
<i>Juan, you're back.</i>

91
00:07:53,548 --> 00:07:55,629
<i>I just made something for you.</i>

92
00:07:55,629 --> 00:07:58,389
<i>Look, do you like it?</i>

93
00:08:00,029 --> 00:08:01,969
<i>I've put all the stuff you like</i>

94
00:08:01,969 --> 00:08:03,589
<i>in this box.</i>

95
00:08:04,389 --> 00:08:07,228
<i>From now on,</i>

96
00:08:08,149 --> 00:08:09,228
<i>it's your treasure box.</i>

97
00:09:28,536 --> 00:09:35,648
<i>[Consent Form for Discontinuing Treatment]</i>

98
00:10:23,236 --> 00:10:25,120
<i>[Family Signature]</i>

99
00:10:36,214 --> 00:10:41,440
<i>[Family Signature]</i>

100
00:10:46,509 --> 00:10:48,413
<i>[Shen Juan]</i>

101
00:10:48,989 --> 00:10:53,188
Shen Juan, are you sure?

102
00:11:03,328 --> 00:11:04,349
Shen Juan.

103
00:11:04,349 --> 00:11:06,649
I want to spend more time

104
00:11:06,649 --> 00:11:07,909
with Uncle Qinghe.

105
00:11:10,428 --> 00:11:11,468
Don't worry.

106
00:11:12,468 --> 00:11:15,948
I will take care of myself and eat well.

107
00:11:18,269 --> 00:11:19,269
So,

108
00:11:22,029 --> 00:11:24,068
please agree to my last request.

109
00:11:28,428 --> 00:11:29,568
Okay.

110
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,512
Thank you.

111
00:11:34,909 --> 00:11:36,256
Shen Juan.

112
00:11:37,668 --> 00:11:39,029
Let him be alone.

113
00:11:40,269 --> 00:11:41,869
He needs to pull himself together on his own.

114
00:12:17,588 --> 00:12:19,608
It's the last day of this semester.

115
00:12:19,608 --> 00:12:20,749
Juan still didn't come.

116
00:12:21,428 --> 00:12:23,029
I called Uncle last night.

117
00:12:24,308 --> 00:12:25,909
He said Uncle Qinghe's condition is not good.

118
00:12:26,948 --> 00:12:28,409
He wants us to enlighten Juan.

119
00:12:28,409 --> 00:12:30,749
But we can't do it.

120
00:12:31,468 --> 00:12:33,468
At this time, Lin Yujing left.

121
00:12:34,068 --> 00:12:35,389
I can't believe her.

122
00:12:37,828 --> 00:12:39,909
But we must do something.

123
00:12:39,909 --> 00:12:41,349
Why don't we pack up his things

124
00:12:41,349 --> 00:12:42,629
and go to his shop first?

125
00:12:44,948 --> 00:12:45,952
Okay.

126
00:13:11,869 --> 00:13:13,088
Juan is back.

127
00:13:14,229 --> 00:13:15,424
Juan.

128
00:13:22,149 --> 00:13:23,468
You must be Shen Juan's classmates.

129
00:13:24,109 --> 00:13:25,349
I'm his father.

130
00:13:26,109 --> 00:13:27,149
Hello, Mr. Shen.

131
00:13:27,149 --> 00:13:28,709
We are Shen Juan's friends.

132
00:13:28,709 --> 00:13:30,029
He hasn't been to school recently,

133
00:13:30,029 --> 00:13:32,629
so he has a lot of homework to do.
We brought it over for him.

134
00:13:32,629 --> 00:13:34,849
Thank you. We just came back from the hospital.

135
00:13:34,849 --> 00:13:36,629
Shen Juan is napping in his room.

136
00:13:43,828 --> 00:13:46,269
Running this shop must be hard, right?

137
00:13:47,349 --> 00:13:48,589
Yes.

138
00:13:48,589 --> 00:13:50,868
This place is not a busy area,

139
00:13:50,868 --> 00:13:53,049
and there aren't many customers.

140
00:13:53,049 --> 00:13:54,329
Juan has to go to school during the day

141
00:13:54,329 --> 00:13:55,468
and run the business at night.

142
00:13:56,349 --> 00:13:58,029
When he couldn't pay the rent,

143
00:13:58,029 --> 00:13:59,509
he was almost kicked out.

144
00:13:59,509 --> 00:14:00,528
After that,

145
00:14:00,528 --> 00:14:02,889
we organized an event with another classmate.

146
00:14:02,889 --> 00:14:04,609
Yes, in that event,

147
00:14:04,609 --> 00:14:06,229
we made two months' rent in one day.

148
00:14:06,229 --> 00:14:07,349
Juan is amazing.

149
00:14:11,149 --> 00:14:12,708
You're awake.

150
00:14:12,708 --> 00:14:14,508
School's out. We brought your books

151
00:14:14,508 --> 00:14:16,389
and the homework.

152
00:14:20,646 --> 00:14:23,678
<i>[Qinghe Silverware]</i>

153
00:14:41,728 --> 00:14:45,223
<i>[Lin Yujing]</i>

154
00:15:05,509 --> 00:15:07,308
<i>At the time of our parting,</i>

155
00:15:08,629 --> 00:15:10,828
<i>I'm already looking forward
to the arrival of reunion.</i>

156
00:15:11,989 --> 00:15:14,629
<i>I believe that parting will not distance us</i>

157
00:15:15,509 --> 00:15:19,068
<i>but make us cherish the time
we spent together even more.</i>

158
00:15:20,588 --> 00:15:24,269
<i>The longer we are apart,
the deeper we will miss each other.</i>

159
00:15:26,188 --> 00:15:28,149
<i>At the time of parting, I made a wish,</i>

160
00:15:28,909 --> 00:15:30,828
<i>hoping that we will remember our promise,</i>

161
00:15:31,788 --> 00:15:33,909
<i>waiting for the day of reunion.</i>

162
00:16:43,029 --> 00:16:46,229
Thank you for coming to honor my uncle.

163
00:17:07,468 --> 00:17:09,829
Alright, I'll see you out.

164
00:17:21,446 --> 00:17:28,789
<i>[Luo Qinghe]</i>

165
00:17:30,708 --> 00:17:31,708
Master,

166
00:17:32,349 --> 00:17:33,668
I came to see you.

167
00:17:46,342 --> 00:17:50,679
<i>[Huaicheng High School]</i>

168
00:17:50,679 --> 00:17:52,309
<i>[Ranking List First Place: Lin Yujing]</i>

169
00:17:52,309 --> 00:17:54,148
It's over, I fell five places.

170
00:17:54,148 --> 00:17:56,309
How am I going to explain this to my parents?

171
00:17:57,149 --> 00:17:58,429
Just tell the truth.

172
00:17:58,429 --> 00:17:59,749
Look at my total score.

173
00:17:59,749 --> 00:18:01,089
I only have three points more than your,

174
00:18:01,089 --> 00:18:02,769
but I'm seven places ahead of you.

175
00:18:02,769 --> 00:18:04,268
My parents won't see it that way.

176
00:18:05,966 --> 00:18:07,928
<i>[Pucheng]</i>

177
00:18:14,054 --> 00:18:17,592
<i>[Pucheng]</i>

178
00:18:29,389 --> 00:18:32,268
You did well in your test.

179
00:18:37,589 --> 00:18:39,629
Has everyone had your test papers?

180
00:18:39,629 --> 00:18:43,228
Everyone writes a test summary.

181
00:18:44,748 --> 00:18:45,748
Any problem?

182
00:18:48,428 --> 00:18:49,609
Look at your test score.

183
00:18:49,609 --> 00:18:50,869
Can you have any problem?

184
00:18:53,629 --> 00:18:55,909
All of you should learn from Lin Yujing.

185
00:18:55,909 --> 00:18:58,789
Whether in quizzes or monthly exams,

186
00:18:58,789 --> 00:19:00,229
she's always the first.

187
00:19:00,229 --> 00:19:01,229
In today's class,

188
00:19:01,229 --> 00:19:03,929
everyone redoes the wrong questions
from the test.

189
00:19:03,929 --> 00:19:05,069
Take out your papers.

190
00:19:14,869 --> 00:19:17,629
Sir, may I borrow your phone? Thank you.

191
00:19:38,149 --> 00:19:40,188
Hello, is this Shen Juan?

192
00:19:42,629 --> 00:19:44,629
Sorry, wrong number.

193
00:20:07,228 --> 00:20:08,769
Hello, is this Shen Juan?

194
00:20:08,769 --> 00:20:10,829
I'm sorry, wrong number.

195
00:20:12,708 --> 00:20:14,629
Sorry, I dialed the wrong number.

196
00:20:54,188 --> 00:20:56,529
<i>Mom, I got out of school early.</i>

197
00:20:56,529 --> 00:20:58,988
I'm right across from you. Come out.

198
00:21:02,948 --> 00:21:03,948
Okay.

199
00:21:14,668 --> 00:21:15,729
You go home.

200
00:21:15,729 --> 00:21:17,748
Your dad and Uncle must have things to do.

201
00:21:18,589 --> 00:21:19,904
It's okay.

202
00:21:20,829 --> 00:21:23,429
Juan, don't keep it all to yourself.

203
00:21:23,429 --> 00:21:24,809
Your body will break down.

204
00:21:24,809 --> 00:21:27,869
How about you take it out on me?

205
00:21:29,869 --> 00:21:30,949
And Lin Yujing--

206
00:21:30,949 --> 00:21:32,384
Stop it.

207
00:21:35,149 --> 00:21:38,109
Your phone seemed to ring just now.

208
00:21:40,748 --> 00:21:42,080
We're leaving.

209
00:21:42,829 --> 00:21:44,032
See you.

210
00:22:06,028 --> 00:22:07,668
<i>Huaicheng</i>

211
00:22:07,668 --> 00:22:08,832
Thank you, sir.

212
00:23:07,428 --> 00:23:08,829
Why did you finish class early today?

213
00:23:09,508 --> 00:23:10,909
I have a stomachache.

214
00:23:11,468 --> 00:23:12,736
Are you okay?

215
00:23:16,708 --> 00:23:17,824
Let's go.

216
00:23:38,909 --> 00:23:42,188
Qinghua, I came to see you.

217
00:23:49,109 --> 00:23:50,528
When I was a kid,

218
00:23:52,069 --> 00:23:53,748
I always looked forward to summer vacation,

219
00:23:55,109 --> 00:23:56,169
because during the summer vacation,

220
00:23:56,169 --> 00:23:57,549
my mom would come back to see me.

221
00:24:00,109 --> 00:24:01,589
Until I was ten,

222
00:24:02,708 --> 00:24:04,508
I knew my mom would never come back.

223
00:24:06,909 --> 00:24:08,349
And you never came back either.

224
00:24:13,152 --> 00:24:14,428
I'm sorry.

225
00:24:16,909 --> 00:24:18,069
My uncle took me

226
00:24:18,069 --> 00:24:20,069
to visit my mom every year.

227
00:24:22,389 --> 00:24:23,669
He always told me

228
00:24:23,669 --> 00:24:26,109
you and my mom have always loved me very much.

229
00:24:26,869 --> 00:24:30,149
You love me and your own careers.

230
00:24:30,988 --> 00:24:33,069
My mom was still fighting for her career

231
00:24:34,309 --> 00:24:36,228
in her last moments of life.

232
00:24:38,268 --> 00:24:39,988
Uncle said he and my mom were the same.

233
00:24:41,909 --> 00:24:45,109
They can dedicate their lives
to their beloved careers.

234
00:24:46,668 --> 00:24:48,829
He said I would understand when I grow up.

235
00:24:49,789 --> 00:24:52,028
Qinghe taught you well.

236
00:24:53,428 --> 00:24:54,720
Juan,

237
00:24:55,668 --> 00:24:59,069
I didn't care enough for you before.

238
00:25:00,149 --> 00:25:01,389
From now on,

239
00:25:01,389 --> 00:25:02,829
I will do my best

240
00:25:03,988 --> 00:25:06,428
to make up for some past regrets.

241
00:25:07,549 --> 00:25:10,228
If you have any difficulties, you can tell me.

242
00:25:12,988 --> 00:25:14,468
I want to discuss with you

243
00:25:16,228 --> 00:25:17,668
about your shop.

244
00:25:18,829 --> 00:25:19,988
Running a shop

245
00:25:20,508 --> 00:25:21,988
takes a lot of effort.

246
00:25:23,268 --> 00:25:24,829
You're going
to take the college entrance exam next year.

247
00:25:25,629 --> 00:25:28,188
It matters to your future.

248
00:25:30,069 --> 00:25:32,589
You might as well focus on preparing for it.

249
00:25:33,109 --> 00:25:36,289
After you get into college, you can consider

250
00:25:36,289 --> 00:25:38,389
whether to continue running this shop.

251
00:25:39,389 --> 00:25:43,468
I'll pay the shop rent for the next two years.

252
00:25:46,909 --> 00:25:48,128
Juan.

253
00:25:49,629 --> 00:25:52,069
It's time to move on.

254
00:25:53,789 --> 00:25:55,508
This is also what Qinghe

255
00:25:56,468 --> 00:25:57,829
and your mom hope for.

256
00:26:16,109 --> 00:26:17,188
Alright.

257
00:26:25,629 --> 00:26:26,668
Dad.

258
00:26:35,789 --> 00:26:36,948
Take good care of yourself.

259
00:26:37,589 --> 00:26:40,629
Okay, you too.

260
00:26:42,228 --> 00:26:43,909
I'll find time to come back to see you.

261
00:27:01,508 --> 00:27:05,309
From now on, it's just the two of us.

262
00:27:20,549 --> 00:27:23,049
You always skip steps.

263
00:27:23,049 --> 00:27:24,349
If you get a wrong answer,

264
00:27:24,349 --> 00:27:25,748
you'll have no scores at all.

265
