270
00:28:24,949 --> 00:28:26,228
<i>The geese are quite fierce.</i>

271
00:28:27,789 --> 00:28:29,508
<i>Who?</i>

272
00:28:29,508 --> 00:28:30,828
<i>He Songnan.</i>

273
00:28:30,828 --> 00:28:32,309
<i>He fed geese?</i>

274
00:28:32,948 --> 00:28:34,549
<i>He was bitten by a goose when he was a kid.</i>

275
00:28:35,708 --> 00:28:36,869
