286
00:28:55,009 --> 00:28:57,209
<i>Then the dog fell into the river,</i>

287
00:28:57,209 --> 00:28:59,009
<i>and the goose bit him on the butt.</i>

288
00:28:59,009 --> 00:29:00,269
<i>He didn't eat a bite</i>

289
00:29:00,269 --> 00:29:02,029
<i>of the stewed goose meat that night.</i>

290
00:29:02,029 --> 00:29:03,508
<i>He was freaked out.</i>

291
00:29:04,028 --> 00:29:05,149
<i>Everyone, be quiet.</i>

292
00:29:07,808 --> 00:29:09,188
<i>Go back to your seat.</i>

293
00:29:33,606 --> 00:29:42,272
<i>[Shen Juan]</i>

294
00:30:36,909 --> 00:30:38,389
<i>I think</i>

295
00:30:38,389 --> 00:30:40,549
<i>it's good to stay here forever.</i>

296
00:30:40,549 --> 00:30:41,629
<i>Then don't leave.</i>

297
00:30:42,629 --> 00:30:43,769
<i>Stay here forever.</i>

298
00:30:43,769 --> 00:30:45,009
<i>Let's both get into Pucheng University.</i>

299
00:30:45,009 --> 00:30:47,789
<i>Okay, it's a deal.</i>

300
00:30:47,789 --> 00:30:49,428
<i>We'll be classmates for four years.</i>

301
00:30:50,829 --> 00:30:52,248
<i>We're so young.</i>

302
00:30:52,248 --> 00:30:53,589
<i>We have a bright future ahead.</i>

303
00:30:55,789 --> 00:30:57,109
<i>And even if we have to part ways,</i>

304
00:30:58,629 --> 00:31:03,309
