308
00:31:21,504 --> 00:31:24,594
<i>♫ I am the paper boat in your heart ♫</i>

309
00:31:24,594 --> 00:31:28,000
<i>♫ And you are my only harbor ♫</i>

310
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:31,836
<i>♫ Time is the sand
slipping through my fingers ♫</i>

311
00:31:31,836 --> 00:31:34,991
<i>♫ Playing the flute of youth ♫</i>

312
00:31:34,991 --> 00:31:38,366
<i>♫ I wait for you to be back ♫</i>

313
00:31:38,366 --> 00:31:41,953
<i>♫ The weary bird returns ♫</i>

314
00:32:22,309 --> 00:32:23,668
I came to see you.

315
00:32:29,589 --> 00:32:31,088
My dad told me

316
00:32:31,088 --> 00:32:32,708
to close the shop

317
00:32:33,829 --> 00:32:34,869
and focus on studying.

318
00:32:38,109 --> 00:32:39,988
I know he's right.

319
00:32:50,149 --> 00:32:51,708
But I just can't bear to close it.

320
00:32:58,309 --> 00:32:59,829
I'm afraid that after closing the shop,

321
00:33:03,589 --> 00:33:05,349
I can't lie to myself anymore

322
00:33:06,869 --> 00:33:08,508
that you're still with me.

323
00:33:39,268 --> 00:33:41,309
Juan, we're back.

324
00:33:46,589 --> 00:33:48,748
Juan, what are you doing?

325
00:33:49,549 --> 00:33:50,829
I'm going to close the shop.

326
00:33:52,109 --> 00:33:53,188
Why?

327
00:33:55,748 --> 00:33:56,989
But it's good to close it.

328
00:33:56,989 --> 00:33:58,468
After all, you will
take the college entrance exam next year.

329
00:33:59,028 --> 00:34:01,349
I'll go back to school next Monday.

330
00:34:01,349 --> 00:34:02,429
Really?

331
00:34:02,429 --> 00:34:03,769
That's great.

332
00:34:03,769 --> 00:34:06,068
Juan, you're finally back.

333
00:34:06,068 --> 00:34:08,949
Juan, I missed you so much.

334
00:34:08,949 --> 00:34:11,329
We've had two monthly exams this month.

335
00:34:11,329 --> 00:34:13,028
Next week is the midterm exam.

336
00:34:14,028 --> 00:34:16,629
Yes, since Lin Yujing left,
you have no competitors.

337
00:34:16,629 --> 00:34:18,909
But you'll meet her
during the college entrance exam.

338
00:34:18,909 --> 00:34:20,409
If you really meet her again,

339
00:34:20,409 --> 00:34:22,248
do you think you can catch up with her?

340
00:34:22,248 --> 00:34:24,369
