342
00:34:25,709 --> 00:34:27,229
Don't mention Lin Yujing.

343
00:34:31,108 --> 00:34:32,369
Are you my buddy?

344
00:34:32,369 --> 00:34:33,829
Why are you always ruining my plans?

345
00:34:36,028 --> 00:34:37,049
Juan.

346
00:34:37,049 --> 00:34:38,689
Look at the dark circles under my eyes.

347
00:34:38,689 --> 00:34:40,389
