356
00:35:02,229 --> 00:35:03,269
Alright.

357
00:35:04,108 --> 00:35:05,588
You're not needed here.

358
00:35:05,588 --> 00:35:07,489
You help me find the cat.

359
00:35:07,489 --> 00:35:08,948
I'm taking it with me.

360
00:35:09,628 --> 00:35:11,548
Okay, leave it to us.

361
00:35:25,468 --> 00:35:27,028
Alright, stop meowing.

362
00:35:27,909 --> 00:35:28,909
If you keep meowing,

363
00:35:30,028 --> 00:35:31,869
