364
00:35:41,988 --> 00:35:43,229
The shop is closed.

365
00:35:45,028 --> 00:35:46,468
My youth has also ended.

366
00:35:48,829 --> 00:35:50,588
Drop the act. Your youth can be revived

367
00:35:50,588 --> 00:35:51,988
