372
00:36:01,669 --> 00:36:02,829
It's just temporarily closed.

373
00:36:04,669 --> 00:36:05,669
Maybe

374
00:36:06,349 --> 00:36:07,429
it'll reopen in the future.

375
00:36:07,429 --> 00:36:08,449
Exactly.

376
00:36:08,449 --> 00:36:10,449
Maybe it'll reopen in the future,

377
00:36:10,449 --> 00:36:11,569
right?

378
00:36:11,569 --> 00:36:13,369
When we've made a lot of money,

379
00:36:13,369 --> 00:36:14,949
